rc=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2780b1bd4c47a11f97e5496964694b9de35697d","tid":132264,"uid":15906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T17:09:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想為佢付出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有無例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好白紙"},{"pid":"830fb2326acd2447cea5e0845c7ecf00ec757d6e","tid":132264,"uid":85564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T17:11:13.000Z","msg":"三個字 乜都想佢好"},{"pid":"0c4b0febd0dea380bf0e57e985c51a64f5e0e088","tid":132264,"uid":15906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T17:12:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n與其提子人，不如諗下自己有乜唔夠好搞到得唔到佢芳心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />愛好簡單，但搵到一個可以比你愛既人就比較難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我仲未搵到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利伸：女神依家有男朋友，但願佢地長相廝守，唔敢奢望能夠同佢發展進一步關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我一直未有過呢種感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有男朋友就應該放棄 重新搵過個啦"},{"pid":"eed991e03f26cb2a406e1400bdb270656fbfdd90","tid":132264,"uid":73202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T17:12:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=wfpCoVbJF1M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwfpCoVbJF1M&d=SZ2g%2FZg1uDubc4iNJejiXjPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=d73911dd\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=wfpCoVbJF1M</a>"},{"pid":"ec0b900754a570b0ef0effb12f7571d70cab0140","tid":132264,"uid":15906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T17:12:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>三個字 乜都想佢好</blockquote><br />\n咁我諗我對所有人都係有咁既想法🤔"},{"pid":"ae46c52d8d4d15ad3881860a8be110a2f3728d71","tid":132264,"uid":2990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T17:13:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想為佢付出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有無例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好白紙</blockquote><br />\n會專登做啲嘢令佢開心，見到佢笑就會覺得好幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4078d691e002cf4eaea28d8223eaa875dbe8406","tid":132264,"uid":82994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T17:15:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n與其提子人，不如諗下自己有乜唔夠好搞到得唔到佢芳心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />愛好簡單，但搵到一個可以比你愛既人就比較難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我仲未搵到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利伸：女神依家有男朋友，但願佢地長相廝守，唔敢奢望能夠同佢發展進一步關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我一直未有過呢種感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有男朋友就應該放棄 重新搵過個啦</blockquote><br />\n或者係feeling啦，覺得佢好似係我想搵既人，真係好愛佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43d8a741a34d46c393d7dd3e9d743561cf2ee54b","tid":132264,"uid":15906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T17:15:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想為佢付出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有無例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好白紙</blockquote><br />\n會專登做啲嘢令佢開心，見到佢笑就會覺得好幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁我諗我有試過🤔平時唔多會幫其他人 但佢有野想我幫我會咩都幫佢搞掂？ 咁樣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b8f035b0ee2ba509208c99336e8a1e61b12d81f","tid":132264,"uid":15906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T17:16:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n與其提子人，不如諗下自己有乜唔夠好搞到得唔到佢芳心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />愛好簡單，但搵到一個可以比你愛既人就比較難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我仲未搵到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利伸：女神依家有男朋友，但願佢地長相廝守，唔敢奢望能夠同佢發展進一步關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我一直未有過呢種感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有男朋友就應該放棄 重新搵過個啦</blockquote><br />\n或者係feeling啦，覺得佢好似係我想搵既人，真係好愛佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n會唔會你圈子少 只係覺得佢好 仲未發現呢個世界仲有其他更岩你既人🤔"},{"pid":"b425fd56bc976e6b5aed5f323f79dc1ee3f6acc4","tid":132264,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T17:17:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>三個字 乜都想佢好</blockquote><br />\n咁我諗我對所有人都係有咁既想法🤔</blockquote><br />\n係撚 你想我死"},{"pid":"493c1f178d914a1b7872542e482cff4051976048","tid":132264,"uid":15906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T17:20:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>三個字 乜都想佢好</blockquote><br />\n咁我諗我對所有人都係有咁既想法🤔</blockquote><br />\n係撚 你想我死</blockquote><br />\n撚有 不過想同你絕交"},{"pid":"ab2f70fe68df54b87e54fec582fbf89d608e0e75","tid":132264,"uid":86901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T17:26:18.000Z","msg":"愛一個人<br />\n甚麼都是，甚麼都不是<br />\n甚麼都有，甚麼都沒有<br />\n甚麼都真實，甚麼都不真實"},{"pid":"f38a28c996b34c4d11cbd314adb63d92798c5d50","tid":132264,"uid":15906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T17:26:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>愛一個人<br />\n甚麼都是，甚麼都不是<br />\n甚麼都有，甚麼都沒有<br />\n甚麼都真實，甚麼都不真實</blockquote><br />\n🤔"},{"pid":"a072699519cf0679ac7797a589e70cbb58f3b1dd","tid":132264,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"