ces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 會唔會太過火</blockquote><br />\n我都唔想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  佔有慾太強 又冇辦法放手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03988f648653515a77b76509414eede83f12349d","tid":132264,"uid":15906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T18:07:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>發生咩事都想佢知道 想同佢分享<br />\n想佢健康 開心 快樂 即使可能要犧牲自己一啲野<br />\n想擁有佢 想佢掛住自己 <br />\n想照顧佢 即使好唔合拍成日鬧交 仍然唔想失去呢個人<br />\n一諗起佢可能有一日會離開自己 會即刻決堤<br />\n<br />\n我覺得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但我覺得以上既野我對每個人都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n普通朋友你都會好想照顧佢 好想留意佢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打係咪好照顧人嗰類型</blockquote><br />\n唔算係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁隨左照顧佢之外 其他野應該無咩大分別</blockquote><br />\n不過愛係好主觀 個個定義唔同<br />\n我反而好難分辨愛同習慣<br />\n或者愛同感激<br />\n定其實呢三樣野總會同時出現</blockquote><br />\n我成日覺得應該係愛&gt;習慣&gt;感激🤔"}]}